{"id":58224,"date":"2024-08-12T00:00:07","date_gmt":"2024-08-11T18:30:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=58224"},"modified":"2024-08-13T17:18:37","modified_gmt":"2024-08-13T11:48:37","slug":"master-bedroom-layout-as-per-vastu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/master-bedroom-layout-as-per-vastu\/","title":{"rendered":"The Ultimate Guide to Design Your Master Bedroom Layout as Per Vastu"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Vastu guidelines to help you get a calm and restful sleep<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever wonder why your master bedroom feels more like a chaotic playground than a peaceful retreat? Perhaps the universe is trying to tell you something. We bring you the principles of Vastu Shastra, the ancient Indian science of architecture, here to rescue your sleep and sanity.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;ve ever rearranged your furniture at 2 a.m. hoping for better vibes or wondered if your bed position is the reason for your weird dreams, this guide is your ticket to serenity. Let&#8217;s dive into the secrets of the perfect master bedroom layout as per Vastu to bring Zen to every corner and promise restful sleep every night. Read on and find your calm!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Master Bedroom Plan as per Vastu: Bed Placement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A well-thought-out master bedroom plan ensures that every aspect of the room contributes to a serene environment. The bed should be placed with the head towards the south or east. This orientation aligns with the earth&#8217;s magnetic field, promoting restful sleep and good health.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/11235602\/master-bedroom-plan-as-per-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Master bedroom Vastu plan: bed placed with head towards south or east for restful sleep and good health\" class=\"wp-image-58231\"